videos.headline: Minter streaks for a 38-yard TD
videos.description: Tra Minter rushes for a 38 yard touchdown to get Southern Alabama on the board.

videos.headline: Luckett bursts for 30-yard TD
videos.description: Ben Luckett rushes 30 yards down the field for a Louisiana Monroe touchdown.

videos.headline: Johnson  rushes 96 yards
videos.description: Xavier Johnson impressively rushes 96 yards to get South Alabama closer to the red zone.

videos.headline: Francis pads South Alabama lead with TD
videos.description: Dallas Davis connects with Maaseiah Francis for a 20-yard touchdown to increase the Jaguars' lead.
